name: Blown Clear (V)
Lore: 'Vader was nearly killed when Han damaged his TIE fighter during a surprise attack in the Death Star trench.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. May place an Imperial Council Member here from hand. Once per turn, if an admiral or logistics agenda here, may subtract X from a starship''s forfeit and immunity to attrition for remainder of turn, where X = total influence at Conference Room.',
